<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 10px; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #e6a817; color: #001f3f; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; }
        .footer { margin-top: 30px; font-size: 12px; color: #888; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Welcome to COA, <%= name %>!</h2>
        <p>Thanks for joining Campus Opportunity Aggregator. To get started and explore personalized opportunities, please verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>
        <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="<%= actionUrl %>" class="btn">Verify Email Address</a>
        </p>
        <p>If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
        <p><small><%= actionUrl %></small></p>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you didn't create an account, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
